# =============================================================================
# NEURONS TOKEN PAYMENT CONFIGURATION
# =============================================================================

# Operator Wallet (Backend)
# --------------------------
# The backend uses this private key to pull Neurons tokens from users
# after they approve spending. This wallet needs BNB for gas (~0.01 BNB).
#
# SECURITY: Keep this private key secure! Only give it permission to call
# transferFrom() - it cannot directly access user funds without approval.
#
# To generate a new wallet:
# 1. Use MetaMask or ethers.js: ethers.Wallet.createRandom()
# 2. Fund it with ~0.01-0.05 BNB for gas (on BNB Chain/BSC)
# 3. Set the address and private key below
#
UATU_OPERATOR_PRIVATE_KEY=0x1234567890abcdef... # REPLACE WITH YOUR OPERATOR WALLET PRIVATE KEY
UATU_OPERATOR_ADDRESS=0x... # REPLACE WITH YOUR OPERATOR WALLET ADDRESS

# Treasury Wallet (Where Revenue Goes)
# -------------------------------------
# Where Neurons tokens are sent after collection. Should be a secure
# cold storage wallet or multisig for production.
#
UATU_TREASURY_ADDRESS=0x... # REPLACE WITH YOUR TREASURY WALLET ADDRESS

# =============================================================================
# PAYMENT FLOW OVERVIEW
# =============================================================================
#
# 1. User sees estimate: 750 Neurons (with 1.5x buffer = 1,125 Neurons reserved)
# 2. Modal prompts: "Approve Uatu to spend up to 1,125 Neurons"
# 3. User approves via MetaMask (must be on BNB Chain)
# 4. Backend checks allowance >= required amount
# 5. Audit starts
# 6. On completion: Backend calls transferFrom(user, treasury, actualCost)
#    using OPERATOR_PRIVATE_KEY
# 7. Exact amount deducted (unused approval stays)
# 8. If payment fails: Create debt, block future audits after grace period
#
# =============================================================================
# GAS COSTS
# =============================================================================
#
# Estimated gas costs on BNB Chain (BSC):
# - approve(): ~50,000 gas (~$0.01-0.02 at normal gas prices)
# - transferFrom(): ~65,000 gas (~$0.02-0.03 at normal gas prices)
#
# Backend pays transferFrom() gas, user pays approve() gas.
#
# =============================================================================
